Package: scoringutils
Title: A collection of proper scoring rules and metrics to assess predictions
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Nikos",
           family = "Bosse",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "nikosbosse@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7750-5280"))
Description: 
    The package bundles a collection of existing metrics and Proper 
    Scoring Rules that can be used to conveniently assess the quality of 
    predictions. Most of the functions are designed to work on predictive samples. 
